# Guide build scaffolding — source photos + verification logs the crib creates
# while researching. NOT site content. Must never be published: GitHub Pages has a
# ~1 GB total-site limit and these _build/ dirs (300+ MB of full-size JPGs) push the
# deploy over it, failing every build with "Page build failed" (dur 0). The cribs read
# _build/ from the shared Drive, not git, so untracking it costs them nothing.
_build/
**/_build/
